lyrics:
Ram thianghlima Lal lo piang chu,
Chung lam arsi chuan a pan zel a;
Mifing amah zawngtute pawh khan,
Arsi chu an en a;
Kei pawh chu arsi eng chu pan zelin,
Lal pianna hmun tawlm Bethlehem min thlen ang.

Aw, Bethlehem tlang ka thlen hma chuan,
Chawl lovin ka kal ang;
Chhun arsi eng chuan min hruai zel ang a
Mari chawi lai nausen chu ka hmu ang a.

Chatuan Salem kawngkhar ropui
Chu ka tan a rawn hawng leh ta e;
Boralna rama leng tawh hnu kha,
Van khua min chantir a;
Lawmin i zai ang, Lal thar a piang ta,
Lei hian chatuan hla mawiin nghawr vel rawh se.

Lawm lo awm ang maw Lal thar chu,
Van mipuite chuan an rawn then ta;
A ngaiin lei an thlir a;
Tapin lei an thlir a.
Chatuan arsi pawhin a um zel a,
A pianna Bethlehem tlang a rawn thlen ta.

Aw, tunah hian i kal ang u,
Hmun khawhar lam chu i pan zel ang;
Lei lal ten amah do mah sela,
Mipuite zawng pawhin;
Kei chu ka Lal duh, ka lunglai hnemtu,
Hmun khawharah pawh aman min awmpui ang.
